<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說釣魚大會的日子，<delay20 />
總覺得讓人好興奮喔～<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的目標是要釣到超多的魚兒，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓<colour id="3" />俞司廷<colour id="65535" />嚇一大跳～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在釣魚大會裡<delay8 />釣越多魚兒，<delay20 />
就能得到越多點數喔～<pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不管什麼樣的魚兒都可以，
你就一條<delay8 />接一條地釣吧～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天我要盡情地享受<delay8 />
參加釣魚大會的樂趣喔～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
就算你看到很大的魚兒的影子，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也不可以太著急喔～<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不管是大魚或小魚，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們跟魚兒的拉拔戰<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都是一樣難的喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00">話說釣魚大會，<delay8 />不是只有釣到的魚兒<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才能兌換成點數嗎～？<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay8 />就算拿以前釣到的魚兒去，<delay20 />
也不能算分啊～<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />如果不是活跳跳的魚兒就不行耶！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你想參加釣魚大會的話，<delay20 />
只要去跟廣場上的<delay8 />
<colour id="3" />俞司廷<colour id="65535" />說就可以囉～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>